# Drop any CSV file here.
# Bharat-Insight will auto-detect, parse, and build the table schema dynamically.
#
# Requirements:
#   - File must end in .csv
#   - First row must be headers
#   - Any number of rows (100K+ supported via virtualization)
#
# Examples:
#   telecom.csv       — TRAI subscriber data
#   digital_india.csv — MeitY scheme data
#   agriculture.csv   — Ministry of Agriculture data
#   any_data.csv      — Platform is fully data-agnostic
